graphql.query:
query companyDetails ($companyID: String!, $parsingOptions: ParsingOptions){
      base: companyDetails(companyID: $companyID, parsingOptions: $parsingOptions){
        id,
        name,
        tagged,
        masked,
        subscribed,
        exported,
        description,
        domain,
        logo,
        fax,
        phone,
        ticker,
        crmEntityId,
        address {
          Street,
          City,
          State,
          Zip,
          street,
          city,
          state,
          zip,
          country,
          latitude,
          longitude,
          CountryCode
        },
        displayAddress,
        employeeCount,
        revenue,
        doziIndustry {
          displayName,
          name,
          isPrimary,
          score
        },
        doziIndustryString,
        revenueRange,
        industry(companyID: $companyID, parsingOptions: $parsingOptions),
        industries: basicIndustries,
        allIndustries,
        isDefunct,
        uniqueCompanyNumContacts,
        companyHref,
        isInPreview,
        funding {
          amountIn000s,
          date,
          type,
          investors {
            companyName
          }
        }
        departmentBudgets {
          departmentType,
          budgetAmount
        }
        certified,
        certificationDate,
        icpScore,
        locationsCount,
        ultimateParent: basicUltimateParent,
        orgImport
      },
      lite: companyDetails(companyID: $companyID, parsingOptions: $parsingOptions){
        entityId,
        address{
          street,
          city,
          zip,
          state,
          country
        },
        displayAddress,
        description,
        NAICS,
        SIC,
        ranking,
        ticker,
        employeeCount,
        employeeCountRange,
        revenue,
        revenueRange,
        companyAttributes{
          areaOfStudy,
          degree,
          displayName,
          attributeCol {
            count,
            description,
            displayName,
            value,
            isPrimary,
            chipHref,
            lastSeen,
            domain
          },
          isOpen,
          isPrimary,
          order
        },
        techAttributes{
          areaOfStudy,
          degree,
          displayName,
          attributeCol {
            count,
            description,
            displayName,
            value,
            isPrimary,
            chipHref,
            lastSeen,
            domain
          },
          isOpen,
          isPrimary,
          order
        },
        industry(companyID: $companyID),
        topIndustry,
        industries{
          displayName,
          value,
          isPrimary,
          chipHref,
          lastSeen,
          domain
        }
        merger {
          companyId,
          companyName,
          zoomUrl
        },
        alternateNames,
        orgChartFacetData {
          ManagementLevels {
            count
          }
        },
        importedData {
          date,
          owners {
            key,
            value {
              date,
              crmEntityId,
              ownerId,
              ownerName
            }
          }
        },
        socialUrls {
          socialMedia {
            followerCount,
            socialNetworkType,
            socialNetworkUrl
          }
        },
        socialUrlsParsed {
          linkedin,
          facebook,
          twitter,
          youtube
        },
        followerCountParsed {
          linkedin,
          facebook,
          twitter,
          youtube
        }
        foundedYear,
        alexaRank,
        departmentBudgets {
          departmentType,
          budgetAmount
        },
        companyEmployeeGrowth {
          oneYearEmployeeGrowthRate,
          twoYearEmployeeGrowthRate,
          employeeGrowthData {
            label,
            employeeCount
          }
        },
        ultimateParent {
          id,
          name
        },
        products {
          value,
          displayName
        },
        technologyAddDrop {
          technologyId,
          activity,
          date,
          logo,
          name
        },
        competitors {
          companyId,
          companyName,
          domain,
          revenue,
          employeeCount
        }
      }
    }

graphql.query:
query suggestions ($rpp: Float!){

          maxResults,
          numUniqueCompanies,
          totalResults,
          data{
            buyingCommittee,
            certifications{
              certificationName,
              organizationName,
            }
            certified,
            companyAddress{
              City,
              CountryCode,
              State,
              Street,
              Zip
            },
            companyDescription,
            companyDomain,
            companyEmployeeCountRange,
            companyEmployees,
            companyID,
            companyLogo,
            companyName,
            companyPhone,
            companyRevenue,
            companyRevenueIn000s,
            companyRevenueRange,
            companyTicker,
            companyType,
            confidenceScore,
            creationDate,
            doziIndustry{
              displayName,
              isPrimary,
              name,
              score
            },
            email,
            firstName,
            isEU,
            isMasked,
            isPast,
            isTagged,
            jobTitle,
            lastMentioned,
            lastName,
            lastUpdatedDate,
            location{
              City,
              CountryCode,
              State,
              Street,
              Zip
            },
            middleInitial,
            mobilePhoneBlocked,
            name,
            noticeProvidedInfo{
              emailNoticeProvidedDate,
              hasBeenNotified
            },
            orgUniversalTagged {
              tagName,
              value
            },
            personID,
            phone,
            positionStartDate,
            profileImageURL,
            score,
            socialUrls{
              socialMedia{
                socialNetworkType,
                socialNetworkUrl
              }
            },
            subscribed,
            title,
            topLevelIndustry,
            universalTagged{
              tagName,
              value
            },
            website
          }
        }
        companySuggestion (rpp: $rpp)
        {
          companiesCount,
          data{
            certificationDate,
            certified,
            companyDescription,
            companyDomain,
            companyID,
            companyIds,
            companyLogo,
            companyName,
            companyPhone,
            companyRevenueIn000s,
            companyType,
            doziIndustry{
              displayName,
              isPrimary,
              score
            },
            employees,
            employeesRange,
            funding{
              amountIn000s,
              date,
              round,
              investors{
                investorName,
                investorDomain
              }
            },
            isDefunct,
            isMasked,
            isTagged,
            location{
              City,
              CountryCode,
              State,
              Street,
              Zip
            },
            orgUniversalTagged {
              tagName,
              value
            },
            revenue,
            revenueRange,
            subscribed,
            topLevelIndustry,
            totalFundingAmountIn000s,
            universalTagged{
              tagName,
              value
            },
            website
          },
          maxResults,
          totalResults
        }
      }
    }

query orgchartsSearch($companyId: String!) {
  orgchartsSearch(

  )

        orgChartSwimLanes {

        data{
            departments,
            jobFunctionName,
            jobFunctions,
            maxResults,

                confidenceScore,

                name,

                isTagged,

                personalEmailAddress,
                subOrgChartTier,
                title,
           
                socialUrls{
                    socialMedia{
                     socialNetworkType,

                },
              
                jobFunctions{
                    department,
                    departmentId,
                    departmentPriority,
                    jobFunctionId,
                    name,
                    orgChartSwimLane,
                    orgChartSwimLanePriority,
                    rank

                solrPseudoOutputFields{

                    listed{
                        listName,
                        value
                    },
                    orgImported,
                    orgOriginSF,
                    owned,
                    recentExported,
                    tagged,

        }
        },
        topLevelContacts{
          businessEmailAddress,
                companyHQPhone,

                directPhone,
                directPhoneIsDoNotCall,
                imageUrl,
                indentationPosition,
                isMasked,
                isTagged,
                personId,
                orgChartTier,
                personalEmailAddress,
                subOrgChartTier,
                name,
                title,
                socialUrls{
                    socialMedia{
                     socialNetworkType,
                     socialNetworkUrl
                    }
                },
              
                jobFunctions{
                    department,
                    departmentId,
                    departmentPriority,
                    jobFunctionId,
                    name,
                    orgChartSwimLane,
                    orgChartSwimLanePriority,
                    rank
                },
                solrPseudoOutputFields{
                    exported,
                    imported,
                    listed{
                        listName,
                        value
                    },
                    orgImported,
                    orgOriginSF,
                    owned,
                    recentExported,
                    tagged,
                    viewed
                }
        }
          
  }
      
}
